OL,3,Vupppppp5CMonday                   G2/4
OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FFour top dermatologists treat
OL,7,     Fpatients for skin conditions such
OL,8,     Fas cysts, lipomas and skin tags
OL,9,     Fthat the NHS views as cosmetic,
OL,10,     Fbut that can hugely affect the
OL,11,     Fsufferers.
OL,12,G0000 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,13,     FA team treats a man found injured
OL,14,     Fin the street. Initially it
OL,15,     Fappears he has been assualted, but
OL,16,     Ffurther investiagtion suggests he
OL,17,     Fmight be a drug user who tried to
OL,18,     Fbreak into a car.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
